| ğŸ”„ **Connection Pooling**  | Reduces latency and overhead from repeatedly opening/closing connections    |
| ğŸ“ˆ **Scalability**         | Handles spikes from autoscaling apps or Lambda concurrency                  |
| ğŸ’¥ **High Availability**   | Continues serving even during DB failovers                                  |
