| ğŸš€ **Better Performance**  | Increases app throughput and reduces DB load                                |
| ğŸ§ª **Failover Management** | Automatically connects to standby DB in Multi-AZ deployments                |
| â˜ï¸ **Serverless Friendly** | Perfect for AWS Lambda + RDS integrations (handles short-lived connections) |


ğŸ’¼ Use Cases
| Scenario                                        | Why Use RDS Proxy                                            |
| ----------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
